headline: MBOLD Launches ‘Protein Catalyst’ to Drive Animal & Plant Protein Innovation in Rapidly Growing Global Protein Industry
summary: Catalyst brings together some of the world’s leading food and agriculture companies, including General Mills, Cargill, Target, Schwan’s Co., SunOpta, and more to pursue protein innovations benefiting farmers, consumers, businesses, planet Catalyst will foster innovation through pre-competitive R&D for animal feed and plant-based proteins; mentorship for protein innovation start-ups; and personalized support for protein companies looking to engage in Minnesota’s vibrant protein ecosystem MINNEAPO
